register.description: This register contains the IP revision code for the PRM part of the PRCM

bitfield.description: Revision Number

register.description: This register provides status on MPU interrupt events. Any event is logged independently of the corresponding IRQENABLE value. SW is required to clear a set bit by writing a '1' into the bit-position to be cleared.

bitfield.description: MM ABB mode change done. This status is set when OPP_CHANGE bit is cleared by hardware in PRM_ABBLDO_MM_CRTL register. It is cleared by SW.
Voltage Controller MM voltage processor command acknowledge status.
Voltage Processor MM transaction completion status. This status is set when a transaction is completed in the voltage processor. It is cleared by SW.
Voltage Processor MM voltage value change event. This status is set when an update has been requested but the new voltage value is the same as the current SMPS voltage value. It is cleared by SW.
Voltage Processor MM timeout event status. This status is set when the timeout occured before the SMPS acknowledge. It is cleared by SW.
Voltage Processor MM voltage higher limit event status. This status is set when the voltage higher limit is reached. It is cleared by SW.
Voltage Processor MM voltage lower limit event status. This status is set when the voltage lower limit is reached. It is cleared by SW.
Voltage Processor MM OPP change done status, including ABB mode change done if applicable (OPP_CHANGE bit cleared in PRM_ABBLDO_MM_CRTL). It is cleared by SW.
Voltage Controller CORE voltage processor command acknowledge status
Voltage Processor CORE transaction completion status. This status is set when a transaction is completed in the voltage processor. It is cleared by SW.
Voltage Processor CORE voltage value change event. This status is set when an update has been requested but the new voltage value is the same as the current SMPS voltage value. It is cleared by SW.
Voltage Processor CORE timeout event status. This status is set when the timeout occured before the SMPS acknowledge. It is cleared by SW.
Voltage Processor CORE voltage higher limit event status. This status is set when the voltage higher limit is reached. It is cleared by SW.
Voltage Processor CORE voltage lower limit event status. This status is set when the voltage lower limit is reached. It is cleared by SW.
Voltage Processor CORE OPP change done status. It is cleared by SW.
Voltage Controller bypass command acknowledge status.
Voltage Controller timeout error event status.
Voltage Controller register address acknowledge error event status.
Voltage Controller slave address acknowledge error event status.
IO pad event interrupt status.

Software supervised transition completed event interrupt status (any domain). Asserted upon completion of any clock domain force wakeup transition or upon completion of any power domain sleep transition with at least one enclosed clock domain configured in forced-sleep.
ABE DPLL recalibration interrupt status.
PER DPLL recalibration interrupt status.
IVA DPLL recalibration interrupt status.
MPU DPLL recalibration interrupt status.
CORE DPLL recalibration interrupt status.
